case_name_full: The People of the State of New York v. Wendy W. Wilkins

opinions.opinion_text:
Appeal from a judgment of the Monroe County Court (Richard A. Keenan, J.), rendered February 8, 2007. The judgment convicted defendant, upon her plea of guilty, of rape in the third degree.
It is hereby ordered that the judgment so appealed from is unanimously affirmed. Present — Smith, J.P., Fahey, Carni, Sconiers and Pine, JJ.

court_short_name: Appellate Division of the Supreme Court of New York
court_full_name: Appellate Division of the Supreme Court of the State of New York
